src:
Strong and Independent: Adorable Golden Retriever Taking Dog-Lead, Walking Itself
Golden retrievers are very smart dogs, but the new generation of dogs keeps getting smarter and smarter. They can even take care of themselves, like this charming girl from the video.

02 Nov 2019, 04:53

Puppies grow up so fast: yesterday you watched a little clumsy pooch taking its first steps and today your little pupster is already a stunning grown-up  dog that can take care of itself. Parents of this beautiful girl from the video put a lot of effort into her upbringing. Now, the doggo is absolutely independent as it can go for a walk herself, not waiting for anybody.
